# 2. Send this EXACT message to that contact on WhatsApp:
#       I allow callmebot to send me messages
# 3. You'll receive an API key back (e.g. 1234567) within 60 seconds
# 4. Fill in your phone number and that API key below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
